{"tha-ap519:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap519:0.2":"Phaladayakavagga ","tha-ap519:0.3":"Kutajapupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap519:1.1":"“Himavantassavidure, ","tha-ap519:1.2":"vasalo nama pabbato; ","tha-ap519:1.3":"Buddho sudassano nama, ","tha-ap519:1.4":"vasate pabbatantare. ","tha-ap519:2.1":"Puppham hemavantam gayha, ","tha-ap519:2.2":"vehasam agamasaham; ","tha-ap519:2.3":"Tatthaddasasim sambuddham, ","tha-ap519:2.4":"oghatinnamanasavam. ","tha-ap519:3.1":"Puppham kutajamadaya, ","tha-ap519:3.2":"sire katvana anjalim; ","tha-ap519:3.3":"Buddhassa abhiropesim, ","tha-ap519:3.4":"sayambhussa mahesino. ","tha-ap519:4.1":"Ekatimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap519:4.2":"yam pupphamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap519:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap519:4.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap519:5.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap519:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap519:5.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap519:6.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap519:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap519:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap519:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap519:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap519:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap519:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma kutajapupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap519:9.1":"Kutajapupphiyattherassapadanam sattamam. "}